  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\n#### ISSUE 1\r\nIf open the `Network fee` bottom sheet and scroll it down the Save button will be stuck to the bottom of the screen.\r\nThe issue is reproduced on 50% of test devices. Could reproduce on iPhone SE, Pixel 2, Galaxy S8.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nMargin below the 'Save' button\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/131637633-96c5d332-7e71-4104-a9ed-1e0730f6448c.mp4\r\n\r\n#### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open Wallet\r\n2. Open `Send transaction` dialog\r\n3. Enter amount and choose receiver\r\n4. Tap `Next` > Tap `Network fee` \r\n5. Scroll down\r\n\r\n#### ISSUE 2\r\n\r\nIf you open the keyboard on the `Network fee` bottom sheet by setting focus on some field, then it will be impossible to scroll the screen to the very top. Some information will be hidden.\r\nThe issue is reproducible on Android devices only.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/131644074-c0176aec-5462-4552-9643-493c7de872bc.mp4\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 01/09\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
